      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING PERCAT (2) dropped out early but hit the line hard, charging into third and beaten 4 lengths win (29.81) at this track in Grade 5. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Overdue and expected to feature again. ZIPPING CRUELLA (3) settled down midfield and held her position to the line when finishing 5th (30.24) at Wentworth Park. Worth following up. TARAWI MALIBU (8) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (29.76) at Gosford behind Exorbitant in a Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Bold showing expected. PINK VENOM (4) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
